* GF180MCU-D pad-limited class-AB common-source RF PA.
* Pins: gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias
* This mirrors the reference RFPA common-source example:
* 250 MHz, 50 ohm external load, high-pass output match, and H2/H3 traps.
.subckt {{netlist_name}} gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias

* Output device: total W ~= 897.6 um with the default M1 settings.
MMOUT drain gate gnda gnda nfet_03v3.12 l={{ M1_L }}u w={{ M1_W }}u m={{ M1_M }}

* Bias and stabilization.
CINBLK rfin gate_in 100p
RGSTOP gate_in gate 3.3
IBIAS vdda drain 10m
RBLEED gate vbias 20k

* AC-coupled high-pass L-match: roughly transforms 50 ohm to 200 ohm.
CBLOCK drain nmatch 100p
RNMATCH nmatch gnda 1G
RCSER nmatch nmatch_cser 1.73
CSER nmatch_cser rfout 7.351p
RLSHUNT rfout lshunt_top 5.77
LSHUNT lshunt_top gnda 73.511n

* Harmonic traps: series-resonant shunts near H2 and H3.
RLH2 rfout h2trap_l 7.96
LH2 h2trap_l h2trap 50.661n
RCH2 h2trap h2trap_c 1.59
CH2 h2trap_c gnda 2p
RLH3 rfout h3trap_l 10.61
LH3 h3trap_l h3trap 45.032n
RCH3 h3trap h3trap_c 2.12
CH3 h3trap_c gnda 1p

.ends {{netlist_name}}
